Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: SteerLLM
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Steer LLM responses towards a certain topic/subject or to enhance rule-play characteristics (ex: personas which are more funny) or to enhance response capabilities (ex: make it provide correct responses to tricky puzzles), using steering vectors by doing activation engineering
Home-page: https://github.com/Mihaiii/SteerLLM
